title: Google Cloud Platform
description: Cloud Architect designs, develops, and manages solutions on Google Cloud.
author: Mwangilwa Zimba

body.raw:
![Image Description](/static/images/gcp.png)


The Google Cloud Consulting portfolio provides a unified services capability, 
bringing together offerings, across multiple specializations, into a single place. 
This includes services from learning to technical account management to professional 
services and customer success.
